# Panduan Dokumentasi Backend SMEGAMART

> Dokumen ini disusun berdasarkan **analisis langsung** terhadap source code project `kasirku`.
> Fokus: **Backend Laravel** — tidak membahas database secara detail.

---

## 1. Ringkasan Kebutuhan Backend

Berdasarkan analisis kode, backend SMEGAMART memiliki komponen-komponen berikut:

| Komponen | Jumlah | Detail |
|---|---|---|
| Controllers | 17 | TransactionController, BookingController, CashierBookingController, ReportController, CashierItemController, StockAdjustmentController, WarehouseController, UserController, dll. |
| Models | 14 | Transaction, Booking, CashierItem, WarehouseItem, StockTransferLog, StockAdjustment, Member, dll. |
| Middleware Custom | 3 | EnsureUserRole, PreventBackHistory, Authenticate |
| Services | 2 | StoreDataService (AI context), GeminiService (AI chat) |
| Exports | 2 | ReportsExport (Excel), PelangganTemplateExport |
| Imports | 1 | PelangganImport |
| Observers | 2 | CashierItemObserver, WarehouseItemObserver |
| Role Pengguna | 3 | admin, kasir, pelanggan |

### Fitur Backend Utama:
1. **Checkout Transaksi POS** — DB::transaction + lockForUpdate + idempotency token
2. **Booking Online** — lifecycle status (pending → confirmed → processing → ready → completed/cancelled) + stock reservation
3. **Transfer Stok** — gudang → kasir dengan log transfer
4. **Stock Opname** — penyesuaian stok kasir dan gudang
5. **Barang Titipan (Consignment)** — lifecycle harian
6. **Laporan & Export** — PDF (DomPDF) + Excel (Maatwebsite)
7. **Role-Based Access Control** — middleware [EnsureUserRole](file:///d:/kasirku/app/Http/Middleware/EnsureUserRole.php#10-33)
8. **Integrasi AI** — Gemini API + StoreDataService

