## 5. Relasi Antar Komponen Backend

### Alur Kerja Utama
```
Browser (Request)
    ↓
routes/web.php  →  Menentukan controller berdasarkan URL dan HTTP method
    ↓
Middleware (auth + role)  →  Memeriksa autentikasi dan hak akses
    ↓
Controller  →  Memproses logika bisnis (validasi, perhitungan, dll)
    ↓
Model (Eloquent ORM)  →  Berinteraksi dengan database via query builder
    ↓
DB::transaction + lockForUpdate  →  Menjaga konsistensi data
    ↓
Response (View / Redirect / JSON)  →  Dikirim kembali ke browser
```

### Relasi Spesifik per Proses

#### Checkout POS
```
Route POST /cashier/transaksi/bayar
  → middleware: auth, role:kasir
  → TransactionController::checkout()
    → validate input (item_id, qty, paid_amount, payment_method, token)
    → DB::transaction {
        → CashierItem::lockForUpdate()     ← mencegah race condition
        → validasi stok real-time
        → Transaction::create()            ← simpan header transaksi
        → TransactionDetail::create()      ← simpan detail per item
        → CashierItem::decrement('stock')  ← kurangi stok
        → session token                    ← cegah double submit
      }
    → redirect ke halaman struk
```

#### Booking Online
```
Route POST /booking/checkout
  → middleware: auth, role:pelanggan
  → BookingController::placeOrder()
    → validate input (delivery_type, address, pickup_time, payment_method)
    → DB::beginTransaction() {
        → CashierItem::lockForUpdate()     ← lock stok
        → CashierItem::decrement('stock')  ← reservasi stok langsung
        → Booking::create()                ← simpan booking
        → BookingItem::create()            ← simpan item booking
      }
    → redirect ke halaman status

Route POST /cashier/bookings/{booking}/accept
  → middleware: auth, role:kasir
  → CashierBookingController::accept()
    → DB::transaction {
        → Booking::lockForUpdate()         ← cegah double-accept
        → update status → 'confirmed'
      }

Route POST /cashier/bookings/{booking}/reject
  → CashierBookingController::reject()
    → DB::transaction {
        → Booking::lockForUpdate()
        → CashierItem::increment('stock')  ← kembalikan stok
        → update status → 'cancelled'
      }
```

#### Transfer Stok
```
Route POST /cashier/stock/warehouse
  → middleware: auth, role:kasir
  → CashierItemController::storeFromWarehouse()
    → validate (warehouse_item_id, quantity, discount)
    → DB::transaction {
        → WarehouseItem::lockForUpdate()   ← lock gudang
        → validasi stok gudang
        → WarehouseItem::decrement()       ← kurangi gudang
        → CashierItem::create/update()     ← tambah ke kasir
        → StockTransferLog::create()       ← catat riwayat
      }
```

#### Laporan & Export
```
Route GET /reports
  → middleware: auth, role:admin
  → ReportController::index()
    → query Transaction + filter (today/week/month/custom/all)
    → filter source (pos/online/all)
    → agregasi: total transaksi, pendapatan, HPP, laba bersih
    → render view

Route GET /reports/export-pdf
  → ReportController::exportPdf()
    → query + Pdf::loadView() → download .pdf

Route GET /reports/export-excel
  → ReportController::exportExcel()
    → query + Excel::download(ReportsExport) → download .xlsx
```

